oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: unknown
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: In front of the Campbell Harrison Walker home (11346 Hardin Valley Road, Knox County, TN). Back row, l-r: Sallie Walker (1869-1941), Margaret Walker Callaway (1882-1965); Carrie Mitchell (Mrs. Campbell H. Walker) (1844-1921); Dora Ann Walker (1871-1949). Front row: John Harvey Calloway (1909- ); Ralph Walker Calloway (1905-1959). Ca. 1920.
